initialize new project with npm init
install parcel npm i parcel@2 -D
npm start 

note bundlers like parcel and webpack will push all the necessary things into distribution file and push to the browser

//when looping through the arrays in ingredients, dont use forEach, use map becuase it returns a new array with equal lenghth.

note: After looping through the entire array, it will return a big string which can be joined 

install polifill: so old browsers can run our app 
npm install core-js regenerator-runtime
